8.20.19  5:14 pm   Do you regret switching to the shittier version of Final Cut?

     it's not clear which one is shittier, but either way that's not quite what happened

      I don't know about you but it's my biggest regret. So much so that i abandoned it and did something i never thought i would. I switched to Windows and started using Premiere some time ago.

     one thing that may surprise you, is that premier, the old final cut, and the new final cut, were all invented/designed by the same person

      I didn't like FCP X but i wish you good luck with it.

     it was incomplete when they first released it. it's probably much different than when you saw it. but another distracting /confusing issue back then was that it was named the same thing as something different

      I hope you get things sorted out and make awesome content again.
